consistent_output:
correct_usage_1("java.io.DataOutputStream", label1, dos_var, in_meth) :- 
    call("java.io.DataOutputStream", label1, dos_var, in_meth), 
    post_dom(label1, in_meth, label_write, in_meth), 
    post_dom(label_write, in_meth, label_close, in_meth).

correct_usage_2("java.io.DataOutputStream", label1, dos_var, in_meth) :- 
    call("java.io.DataOutputStream", label1, dos_var, in_meth), 
    flow_reach(label_try, in_meth, label1, in_meth), 
    flow_reach(label1, in_meth, label_catch_begin, in_meth).

correct_write_usage("java.io.DataOutputStream.write*", label_write, dos_var_write, in_meth) :-
    call("java.io.DataOutputStream.write*", label_write, dos_var_write, in_meth), 
    dom(label_write, in_meth, label1, in_meth).

correct_write_condition(label_write, dos_var_write, in_meth) :- 
    actual_argument(_, _, label_write, _, in_meth), 
    variable(dos_var_write, in_meth).

correct_close_usage("java.io.DataOutputStream.close", label_close, dos_var_close, in_meth) :-
    call("java.io.DataOutputStream.close", label_close, dos_var_close, in_meth), 
    dom(label_close, in_meth, label_write, in_meth).

correct_try_usage("try", label_try, in_meth) :-
    try(label_try, _, in_meth).

correct_catch_usage("catch", label_catch_begin, in_meth) :-
    catch(_, _, label_catch_begin, _, _, in_meth).

v_condition(dos_var, label1, in_meth) :- 
    correct_write_condition(_, dos_var, in_meth);
    correct_close_usage(_, label1, dos_var, in_meth).
